info.author: Wade Dismukes
info.description:
treeducken_tools
========

This software is a package of functions to make using the treeducken simulation software
(see http://github.com/wadedismukes/treeducken) easier. Includedd within are functions that
allow users to run the software, create settings files, and determine parameters for simulations.
In addition, there is a wrapper for the Seq-Gen software. 

The setup of treeducken_tools is based on the Shablona template project for small scientific Python projects. 
See more at http://github.com/uwescience/shablona. This templatecontains infrastructure for testing, documentation,
continuous integration and deployment, which can be easily adapted
to use in other projects.

To learn more about this project, please go to the
repository README_.
.. _README: https://github.com/wadedismukes/treeducken_tools/master/README.md
License
